      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"now\" part feels so hollow though. like, why bother building anything or trying to find meaning when the end result is literally zero? the math just doesn't add up. it feels like we're just performing a play for an empty theater. if the logic is that everything eventually disappears, then any effort to resist that is just exhausting. its like forcing yourself to stay in a movie you know is going to end in total darkness regardless of how you act.",
